其實間間bank都有rental reimbursement <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1fd6a132d7906e631c551146d8605bdc4d41763","tid":959304,"uid":12661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T12:48:47.000Z","msg":"呢啲日常香港商業常識嚟&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n打工仔收一份糧（無租金津貼），薪奉稅課税金額等於嗰份糧。如果收糧之餘，再有租金津貼（自住），課稅金額一般定為份糧x110％（無論租金津貼金額多少）。<br />\n<br />\n香港租金貴，以上安排算係政府體恤租樓打工仔嘅政策。<br />\n<br />\n從僱主角度，無論出糧定提供租金津貼畀員工，都會被視為為咗賺取利潤而作出嘅開銷，稅務上並無分別，所以唔會有額外財務成本。不過，有一定行政成本。另外，如果打工仔故意將自己（或者親屬）嘅樓，租返畀自己以獲得以上稅務優惠，可能構成逃稅。僱主幫佢咁用，亦可能惹上麻煩。"},{"pid":"c4ecbe494733f44f04682285280c013c2d4c0c75","tid":959304,"uid":107470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:01:15.000Z","msg":"原來係減稅用<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 學到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cb5796da7ac41bbf9615eb18da2f19164f28759","tid":959304,"uid":65378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:02:20.000Z","msg":"唔洗打卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}